These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: hiking, reading, skydiving, writing
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, goldfish, goat, hamster
There are 4 different favourite colors: grey, red, apricot, ivory
1. the person who likes grey is the person who's hobby is writing##1
2. the person who likes apricot is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
3. the person who's hobby is writing is in an odd position##4
4. the person who likes red is on the left or right of the person who likes ivory##3
5. the owner of the goat is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is hiking##3
6. the person who likes ivory is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
7. the person who likes red is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person who likes ivory is between the owner of the hamster and the person who's hobby is hiking##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |   2    |    3    |     4     |
| Hobby         | writing      | hiking | reading | skydiving |
| Pet   | goat | chinchilla  | goldfish   | hamster    |
| Color     | grey     | apricot    | ivory    | red      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-2::.
4 different pets are kept: ferret, rat, hamster, horse
There are 4 different nationalities: american, japanese, mexican, polish
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, 7up, juice, iced-tea
1. the person drinking 7up is on the left or right of the owner of the hamster##3
2. the owner of the horse is the mexican##1
3. the owner of the hamster is in an even position##4
4. the person drinking water is on the far right##1
5. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far left##1
6. the owner of the rat is on the left of the japanese##1
7. the american is between the owner of the horse and the owner of the rat##2
8. the polish is between the japanese and the owner of the hamster##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |    4     |
| Pet         | horse | hamster   | rat | ferret  |
| Nationality   | mexican     | american | polish  | japanese |
| Beverage     | iced-tea        | juice  | 7up    | water |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, iced-tea, sprite, juice
The people have 4 different jobs:  coach, pilot, fisherman, scientist
The people use 4 different means of transport: motorbike, roller, snowmobile, train
1. the scientist is between the person drinking hot-chocolate and the person drinking juice##2
2. the pilot is the person driving the train##1
3. the person driving the motorbike is the person drinking sprite##1
4. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
5. the person drinking juice is in an odd position##4
6. the fisherman is between the person drinking iced-tea and the coach##2
7. the scientist is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4     |
| Beverage          | hot-chocolate | iced-tea   | juice     | sprite     |
| Job   | pilot  | scientist | fisherman   | coach  |
| Transport     | train      | roller | snowmobile | motorbike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-4::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, tram, ship, subway
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: pop, punk, salsa, soul
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: march, july, april, november
1. the fan of soul is in an even position##4
2. the person driving the tram is the person who's birthday is in july##1
3. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
4. the fan of punk is on the left or right of the person driving the ship##3
5. the fan of soul is the person who's birthday is in march##1
6. the person driving the ship is the fan of pop##1
7. the fan of salsa is the person driving the bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Transport   | bike  | subway   | ship     | tram |
| Music-Genre   | salsa  | soul      | pop        | punk     |
| Birthday         | april | march | november | july   |

