.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-5::.
4 different pets are kept: lizard, pony, guinea-pig, dog
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: golf, rugby, swimming, volleyball
The people have 4 different jobs:  doctor, coach, manager, pilot
1. the owner of the dog is the person who's sport is volleyball##1
2. the owner of the guinea-pig is in an odd position##4
3. the doctor is the person who's sport is volleyball##1
4. the coach is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
5. the doctor is in an even position##4
6. the person who's sport is rugby is on the far left##1
7. the owner of the pony is on the far right##1
8. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left or right of the manager##3
9. the person who's sport is golf is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |    4     |
| Pet   | lizard   | dog   | guinea-pig | pony |
| Sport         | rugby      | volleyball | golf      | swimming |
| Job     | coach | doctor        | pilot       | manager  |

