.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-6::.
House: wooden, modern, tower, victorian
The people have 4 different jobs:  musician, project-manager, photographer, entrepreneur
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, guinea-pig, hamster, rat
1. the modern house is in an odd position##4
2. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the photographer##1
3. the owner of the chinchilla is the modern house##1
4. the tower house is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
5. the project-manager is on the far right##1
6. the victorian house is on the left of the modern house##1
7. the victorian house is in an even position##4
8. the entrepreneur is on the right of the musician##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2      |     3      |    4    |
| House    | tower   | victorian      | modern       | wooden |
| Job   | musician | entrepreneur | photographer     | project-manager |
| Pet     | rat     | guinea-pig  | chinchilla | hamster |

