.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-7::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, old-henry, dunhill, siglo
City: nizza, san-francisco, paris, rome
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, goat, guinea-pig, horse
1. the owner of the guinea-pig is the person traveling to nizza##1
2. the owner of the goat is between the person traveling to rome and the owner of the chinchilla##2
3. the person traveling to rome is the old-henry-smoker##1
4. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left or right of the old-henry-smoker##3
5. the swisher-smoker is in an even position##4
6. the person traveling to rome is on the right of the siglo-smoker##1
7. the person traveling to nizza is the swisher-smoker##1
8. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |       3       |     4      |
| Cigar      | dunhill   | siglo          | old-henry | swisher        |
| City   | paris     | san-francisco | rome   | nizza     |
| Pet           | chinchilla | goat         | horse         | guinea-pig |

