.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-8::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, september, july, april
There are 4 different nationalities: malaysian, australian, japanese, brazilian
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, disco, electronic, house
1. the fan of house is on the left or right of the fan of electronic##3
2. the japanese is the person who's birthday is in november##1
3. the brazilian is the person who's birthday is in july##1
4. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
5. the fan of disco is between the malaysian and the person who's birthday is in november##2
6. the fan of house is on the left or right of the japanese##3
7. the person who's birthday is in november is in an even position##4
8. the person who's birthday is in november is between the person who's birthday is in september and the person who's birthday is in july##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |     4      |
| Birthday         | september | november      | july       | april    |
| Nationality           | australian  | japanese  | brazilian | malaysian |
| Music-Genre   | house      | electronic | disco         | country    |

