.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-9::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, fanta, iced-tea, water
There 4 different types of food: carrot, papaya, onion, lettuce
House: palace, ranch-style, farmhouse, colonial
1. the person eating carrot is in an odd position##4
2. the person drinking coffee is on the left or right of the person eating carrot##3
3. the person drinking water is on the left or right of the person eating carrot##3
4. the ranch-style house is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
5. the person drinking fanta is on the left or right of the farmhouse house##3
6. the colonial house is on the right of the person eating carrot##1
7. the person eating carrot is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
8. the person eating papaya is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
9. the person eating lettuce is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |      3       |       4       |
| Beverage   | fanta         | coffee  | iced-tea     | water         |
| Food        | lettuce | papaya | carrot | onion         |
| House      | ranch-style         | farmhouse  | palace   | colonial |

