.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-10::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: comedy, sports, martial-arts, scientific
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, malaysian, nigerian, turkish
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, dannemann, swisher, tiparillo
 1. the swisher-smoker is on the left or right of the person watching martial-arts movies##3
 2. the canadian is on the far left or far right##3
 3. the dannemann-smoker is on the right of the person watching sports movies##1
 4. the nigerian is between the person watching sports movies and the person watching comedy movies##2
 5. the tiparillo-smoker is on the left or right of the person watching sports movies##3
 6. the tiparillo-smoker is the person watching martial-arts movies##1
 7. the turkish is on the far right##1
 8. the person watching comedy movies is in an odd position##4
 9. the malaysian is between the person watching scientific movies and the person watching martial-arts movies##2
10. the swisher-smoker is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy  | martial-arts    | sports | scientific    |
| Nationality   | canadian | nigerian | malaysian  | turkish |
| Cigar           | swisher   | tiparillo    | old-henry        | dannemann   |

