.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-11::.
City: marseilles, new-york, hannover, paris
House: art-deco, gothic-revival, futuristic, craftsman
There are 4 different nationalities: dutch, indonesian, italian, russian
1. the person traveling to marseilles is on the far left or far right##3
2. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the art-deco house##1
3. the russian is on the left or right of the futuristic house##3
4. the gothic-revival house is in an even position##4
5. the person traveling to hannover is on the right of the art-deco house##1
6. the russian is on the right of the gothic-revival house##1
7. the indonesian is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1
8. the person traveling to paris is on the left or right of the indonesian##3
9. the person traveling to marseilles is on the left of the dutch##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| City      | marseilles                | paris  | new-york | hannover   |
| House           | craftsman | gothic-revival | art-deco   | futuristic |
| Nationality   | indonesian         | dutch     | russian     | italian |

