.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-12::.
City: prague, paris, rome, venice
The people use 4 different means of transport: snowmobile, airplane, quad-bike, bike
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: d&b, dubstep, jazz, r&b
1. the person traveling to paris is on the left of the person traveling to venice##1
2. the person traveling to rome is on the far left##1
3. the fan of dubstep is on the left or right of the fan of r&b##3
4. the person traveling to rome is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
5. the fan of d&b is between the person driving the bike and the fan of r&b##2
6. the person driving the quad-bike is in an even position##4
7. the person traveling to prague is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |   3    |    4    |
| City          | rome    | paris  | venice  | prague |
| Transport   | bike | airplane | snowmobile | quad-bike |
| Music-Genre   | jazz    | d&b     | r&b    | dubstep |

