.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-13::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daffodil, amaryllis, sunflower, aconite
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, australian, pakistani, turkish
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, havana, pall-mall, baccarat
1. the havana-smoker is between the person who growssunflower and the argentine##2
2. the person who growsdaffodil is on the far left or far right##3
3. the pakistani is on the left or right of the pall-mall-smoker##3
4. the baccarat-smoker is on the left of the australian##1
5. the baccarat-smoker is in an odd position##4
6. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left or right of the pall-mall-smoker##3
7. the argentine is on the left or right of the turkish##3
8. the pakistani is the person who growsdaffodil##1
9. the turkish is between the pall-mall-smoker and the cain-smoker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3    |     4     |
| Flower      | daffodil | sunflower      | amaryllis  | aconite    |
| Nationality   | pakistani   | australian | turkish | argentine |
| Cigar           | baccarat      | pall-mall       | havana   | cain      |

