.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-14::.
4 different pets are kept: goat, rabbit, fish, rat
4 different games are played: backgammon, whist, canasta, scrabble
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, golf, handball, lacrosse
1. the owner of the fish is in an even position##4
2. the owner of the rabbit is between the owner of the rat and the person who's sport is cycling##2
3. the person who's sport is golf is on the far left or far right##3
4. the owner of the rat is in an even position##4
5. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
6. the person playing scrabble is between the person who's sport is cycling and the person playing backgammon##2
7. the person who's sport is golf is on the far right##1
8. the person playing whist is in an even position##4
9. the person who's sport is cycling is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |    3     |     4      |
| Pet         | goat    | fish | rabbit  | rat  |
| Game   | canasta | whist       | scrabble | backgammon |
| Sport         | handball   | cycling      | lacrosse | golf       |

