.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-15::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, almond-milk, cola, tea
The people have 4 different jobs:  designer, musician, manager, doctor
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: dahlia, azalea, tulip, iris
1. the person who growsazalea is in an even position##4
2. the person who growsazalea is the person drinking almond-milk##1
3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the musician##1
4. the person drinking cola is the doctor##1
5. the person drinking cola is on the far left##1
6. the designer is the person who growsazalea##1
7. the person who growsdahlia is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
8. the person who growsiris is the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3    |   4    |
| Beverage      | cola      | almond-milk | 7up     | tea    |
| Job   | doctor | designer      | musician | manager |
| Flower           | tulip   | azalea  | dahlia     | iris |

