.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-16::.
There 4 different types of food: garlic, radish, grapes, strawberry
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, surfing, swimming, water-polo
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, spy, adventure, documentary
1. the person eating garlic is on the left or right of the person eating radish##3
2. the person who's sport is baseball is in an even position##4
3. the person watching documentary movies is on the far left##1
4. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left or right of the person eating strawberry##3
5. the person eating radish is between the person watching spy movies and the person who's sport is swimming##2
6. the person watching action movies is the person who's sport is water-polo##1
7. the person eating radish is on the left of the person eating garlic##1
8. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the person eating garlic##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Food    | grapes    | radish     | garlic    | strawberry        |
| Sport       | swimming   | baseball | surfing | water-polo |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | adventure      | spy    | action   |

