4. the person playing monopoly is on the far left or far right##3
5. the ranch-style house is on the left of the tower house##1
6. the person playing monopoly is in an odd position##4
7. the gothic-revival house is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person playing go is the person watching spy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |     3     |    4     |
| Game          | monopoly | go  | chess   | canasta    |
| Movie-Genre   | animation  | spy     | superhero | disaster |
| House   | gothic-revival   | colonial | ranch-style | tower   |

