3. the person playing chess is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
4. the person who's hobby is reading is the person playing billiard##1
5. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the right of the person who's sport is swimming##1
6. the person playing chess is in an odd position##4
7. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1
8. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |     3      |        4        |
| Hobby         | skydiving | reading   | cooking    | magic-tricks    |
| Game           | backgammon   | billiard    | chess | mah-jongg |
| Sport   | weightlifting    | swimming | lacrosse    | skiing         |

