.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-20::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: sailing, parkour, cricket, tennis
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, bongani, dunhill, blend
4 different pets are kept: bird, horse, mouse, pony
1. the person who's sport is sailing is in an odd position##4
2. the blend-smoker is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the bird is on the left or right of the cain-smoker##3
4. the person who's sport is cricket is on the far left##1
5. the person who's sport is parkour is between the blend-smoker and the cain-smoker##2
6. the bongani-smoker is on the left of the cain-smoker##1
7. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the person who's sport is sailing##1
8. the owner of the horse is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2      |   3    |      4      |
| Sport    | cricket    | parkour    | sailing  | tennis |
| Cigar   | blend | bongani | cain | dunhill      |
| Pet     | horse   | bird        | pony   | mouse       |

 